{"tid":1976724,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國2014年呢件事可以證明香港人最沒資格跟從韓流同韓國文化!","createTime":"2020-04-17T12:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:11:58.000Z","uid":56701,"like":16,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0ff18d271fd2f13bf2125e504ab79d815f416b","tid":1976724,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uu7h5umqld4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUu7h5umqld4&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU91QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=ad140cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uu7h5umqld4</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為當年世越號事件好多香港人响高登度不斷祝賀人地韓國:冚家鏟,絶後,泡菜就是抵死呢類說話! </span><br />\n<br />\n我到而家都好記得高登啲人係幾咁反韓,人地發生災難令我明白到香港人好多都係無乜人性可言!<br />\n<br />\n根本<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人個底就只係跟蹤日本潮流既哈巴狗</span>...同韓國嘢係無關...只係因為連日本人都帶起韓流之後...香港人先突然跟隨! <br />\n韓國人幫手 反送中...而家仲有無人記得? 無啦...變晒做Condom 啦! <br />\n如果而家 可以出返去旅行 ...日本啲魚生食到絶種都得呀香港人!*(不論黃藍! )<br />\n<br />\n最後我可以理直氣壯咁講句:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香 港 人 就 係 反 韓! </div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔會响度講咩世越號既死難者安息等等廢話...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我會希望佢地唔會再降生落呢個有任何香港人同支那人既世界!</span>"},{"pid":"2fcc5b27c294a19b2f6bcfb879c1b1eb5a850510","tid":1976724,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"有用post 推"},{"pid":"50118becc6f7ff177a6fd20cc5072186dd9c328a","tid":1976724,"uid":136738,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:19:16.000Z","msg":"香港人=中國人<br />\n基本啦"},{"pid":"8e2b7cec9815e52e535a20474f3d894225643b80","tid":1976724,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7a0ff18d271fd2f13bf2125e504ab79d815f416b","tid":1976724,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T12:14:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http